  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Methylprednisolone Per os Versus IV for the Treatment of Multiple Sclerosis (MS) Relapses</brief_title>
  <acronym>COPOUSEP</acronym>
  <official_title>Randomised Double-blinded Trial Comparing Efficacy and Safety of Methylprednisolone Per os Versus IV for the Treatment of Multiple Sclerosis Relapses</official_title>
  <sponsors>
